The Telegraph - Calcutta : Nation

 Adult TV 

 New Delhi, May 8: Adult content will be allowed on television late at night if a panel clears a proposal. 

 The government has told the Lok Sabha that a panel is looking into the proposal to introduce watershed timings for adult movies on TV.




